	Volumes:        2 (4 configured)
	Plexes:         3 (8 configured)
	Subdisks:       3 (16 configured)
	
	D a                     State: up       Device /dev/da3h        Avail: 1549/2573 MB (60%)
	D b                     State: up       Device /dev/da4h        Avail: 2061/2573 MB (80%)

